{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"zotero":1,"inscriptions":5},{"title":2,"date":3,"citation":4},"L'epigrafe dall'area del Tempio ellenistico-romano","2017","\u003Cspan>G. Vallarino, «L’epigrafe dall’area del Tempio ellenistico-romano», in \u003Ci>Agrigento. Nuove ricerche sull’area pubblica centrale\u003C/i>, a c. di L.M. Caliò et al. (Rome: Edizioni Quasar, 2017), 123–26\u003C/span>",[6],{"file":7,"uri":7,"title":8,"status":9,"editionAuthor":11,"type":12,"objectType":17,"material":21,"condition":25,"layoutDesc":26,"handNote":33,"date":48,"places":53,"geo":62,"provenance":55,"provenanceGeo":66,"country":69,"region":70,"settlement":59,"repository":71,"idno":75,"textLang":77,"tmNumber":25,"facsimile":81,"letterHeights":88,"publications":89,"zotero":94,"keywords":99,"html":110,"bibl":111},"ISic004373","Dedication by a curator of the res publica Liparitanorum",{"_":10},"draft",null,{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15,"cert":16},"Honorific","#function.honorific","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/69.html","low",{"_":18,"ana":19,"ref":20},"plaque","#object.plaque","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/259",{"_":22,"ana":23,"ref":24},"marble","#material.stone.marble","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/48.html","",{"layout":27},{"p":28,"rs":29,"damage":25},"The remains of six evenly spaced lines of Latin letters are preserved, with a regular left margin; the right margin is not preserved for any line",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},"chiselled","#execution.chiselled","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1",{"lettering":34,"dimensions":35},"The letters are well cut in a relatively refined v-cut, with modest serifs. The letters are tend towards the tall and narrow and are very regular and evenly spaced.  P and R are open, O is somewhat ovoid, E has bars of equal length, D is quite full, the diagonal of the N does not always start from the top of the first hasta. Interpuncts are not consiste